Sasol to Build a $261 Million Gas Power Plant at Sasolburg in South Africa

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-13T13:15:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/sasol-to-build-a-261-million-gas-power-plant-at-sasolburg-in-south-africa.html
Sasol Ltd. (SOL)  said it plans to build a
1.8 billion rand “gas engine power plant” near its existing
electricity generation facilities at Sasolburg in  South Africa .  Building work is scheduled to begin this month and the
project is expected to start producing electricity by the end of
next year, Sasol said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  